+'******************************************************
+'****  BALL ROLLING AND DROP SOUNDS
+'******************************************************
+'
+' Be sure to call RollingUpdate in a timer with a 10ms interval see the GameTimer_Timer() sub
+
+Dim ArchHit
+
+Sub phys_toparch_hit
